Hi,
Try this command:
#######################################
##sudo ln -s /dev/ttyACM0 /dev/ttyS80##
#######################################
and use ttyS80, other option is pi4j for work directly with ttyAMA0
http://pi4j.com/example/serial.html
i tested sucessfully pi4j for communicate raspi and arduino.
